 2012-13552012-10-11,  DFAIT,  ,  , 
ActAppropriation Act No. 3, 2012-13
PrecisAppointment of : JON ALLEN as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Spain and Ambassador of Canada to the Principality of Andorra, with residence in Madrid; PHILIP CALVERT as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Thailand; as Ambassador of Canada to the Lao People's Democratic Republic, with residence in Bangkok and as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Cambodia, with residence in Bangkok; PIERRE GIROUX as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of El Salvador; MICHAEL GRANT as Ambassador of Canada to Libya; RICHARD HANLEY as High Commissioner for Canada to Barbados; as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of Dominica, with residence in Bridgetown; as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of Grenada, with residence in Bridgetwon; as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of Antigua and Barbuda, with residence in Bridgetown; as High Commissioner for Canada to the Federation of St. Kitts and Nevis, with residence in Bridgetown and as High Commissioner for Canada to Montserrat, with residence in Bridgetown; ALEXANDRE LÉVÊQUE as High Commissioner for Canada to the United Republic of Tanzania; as High Commissioner for Canada to the United Republic of Seychelles, with residence in Der-es-Salaam and Ambassador of Canada to the Union of the Comoros, with residence in Der-es-Salaam; ROSS MILLER as Consul General of Canada in Dubai, United Arab Emirates; DENIS ROBERT as Ambassador of Canada to the Grand Duchy of Luxembourg, with residence in Brussels.
